platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: We love finding and pinning creative ideas, tasty recipes, and more. Pinterest’s wonderfully designed app is a constant source of inspiration, whether you’re planning a trip, remodeling your home, or finding something to wear. With a bevy of helpful features—from collaborative boards to built-in messaging—Pinterest is an exceptionally visual way to explore what matters to you.
這款設計精美的 App，除了能讓你尋找創意想法並將其置頂，還提供協作空間、內置訊息和其他實用功能，助你簡單直接地探索有興趣的內容。

Find and pin creative ideas creative ideas with this wonderfully designed app, alongside collaborative boards, built-in messaging and other helpful features to help you visually explore what matters to you.
創造的なアイデアを見つけて保存できる、優れたデザインのアプリです。共同作業ができるボードや内蔵のメッセージに加え、気になっているものを視覚的に探せる便利な機能が多数そろっています。
Find and pin creative ideas with this wonderfully designed app, alongside collaborative boards, built-in messaging, and other helpful features to help you visually explore what matters to you.
這款 App 能幫助你發掘和收藏好點子，並透過可協作的版面和內建訊息等實用功能，輕鬆探索能啟發你的視覺靈感。

Trouvez et épinglez des idées créatives grâce au design magnifique de cette app. Profitez aussi de tableaux collaboratifs, d’une messagerie intégrée et d’autres fonctionnalités utiles pour visualiser toutes vos envies.
